column5: May your bowl overflow with chicken soup and your plate be full of brisket and such.  Roy-when should we expect you ??
Maybe you can come here instead....we can crack open a beer and bid each other a Shana Tova.
Don't forget to have your apples drenched in honey, lol Maybe head over to Yittzi's for a corned beef sandwich, lol  Shana Tova
Wish I could Homie. Gots family in from To. Then again I heard J makes the bestest matzo ball soup this side of............so I just may.
J also make about the best zuchini relish you'll ever come across too darsky
